	<!--"Angry Dragon" Sniper Cannon-->
	<ThingDef ParentName="BuildingBase">
		<defName>RI_Turret_BigSniperTurrent</defName>
		<label>"Flood Dragon" sniper turret</label>
		<description>"Flood Dragon" sniper turret is a highly effective yet logistically demanding large turret. Built upon advanced firearm technology, it boasts an exceptionally long range while maintaining deadly accuracy and firepower.\n\nThis turret consumes Spiritual crystal as ammunition but also contains power-consuming components, requiring electricity.</description>
